notes=Vendored verbatim. The only modification is appending an empty [workspace] table to Cargo.toml to opt out of any parent workspace discovery. The fixture name `dex-liquidity-pool` matches upstream rather than the originally-planned `dex-soroswap`: the Soroswap repo is genuinely multi-contract (factory + library + pair + router + token), and bringing up just the AMM `pair` contract was not tractable inside the Task 1.6 time-box. Soroswap remains a Phase 2 expansion target. soroban-examples liquidity_pool exercises the same AMM patterns (swap + LP-share mint/burn + fee accumulation) as a single self-contained contract.
